title: Midnight in the Desert with Heather Wade - 01-14, 2016.mp3
description:
So there's a problem with this one. I'm missing parts of the show. Only the beginning part though, approximately 15 minutes from the top. I have two different streams recording and they both had an issue. I'm not sure as to why that happened. 

I can rule out a power interruption or a lack of incoming internet, but then again, my router may have performed a reboot (to which I didn't ask it to) I also checked the devices that were recording the streams and their settings (time and crontab) were operating normally. 


Suffice it to say, this is why I don't feel all that comfortable filling in for missing episodes. Because I can't always guarantee that my episodes will be complete. 

Anyway, I can and will fill, but I certainly don't want to be relied upon, as I'm doing this because I'm able to, and as you all can see this time, I wasn't able to deliver a complete show. 

I'm guessing there might have been a problem with the stream? Possibly? If someone listens live, can the comment about that? If not, enjoy what I have and I'll be back to do other fills if I can. Hopefully someone else will be able to give a complete account of this episode. 

Thanks
